      <title>民主党高层称拜登不能忽视美国印度谋杀阴谋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/biden-can-t-ignore-india-murder-plot-in-us-top-democrat-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位民主党高级参议员表示，拜登政府不应该优先考虑与印度的地缘政治关系，而应该要求印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪追究那些涉嫌在美国领土上暗杀美国公民的幕后黑手的责任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/biden-can-t-ignore-india-murder-plot-in-us-top-democrat-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 04:50:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾谴责中国在海上冲突中受伤的举动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/philippines-blasts-china-s-moves-after-sea-clash-injured-sailor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是菲律宾和中国在南海发生的最严重冲突之一，导致一名菲律宾海军人员受重伤。菲律宾呼吁中国尊重其主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/philippines-blasts-china-s-moves-after-sea-clash-injured-sailor</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 04:38:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据俄罗斯文传电讯社报道，俄罗斯法院以盗窃罪判处美国士兵监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/russian-court-sentences-us-soldier-to-jail-for-theft-interfax-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名俄罗斯法官裁定美国中士戈登·布莱克犯有盗窃罪，并对他探访的一名当地妇女发出死亡威胁，此举进一步增加了在该国关押的美国人数量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/russian-court-sentences-us-soldier-to-jail-for-theft-interfax-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 04:29:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>私立学校因工党税收计划威胁削减低收入学生援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/labour-s-private-school-vat-plan-may-prompt-cuts-in-bursaries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些学校表示，如果工党坚持对学校征收增值税，他们将不得不削减帮助低收入家庭的助学金项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/labour-s-private-school-vat-plan-may-prompt-cuts-in-bursaries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 04:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将抨击法国预算赤字，加剧政治困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/eu-to-slam-france-over-budget-deficit-adding-to-political-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在立法选举开始前不到两周，欧盟将对法国违反欧盟赤字和债务规则进行谴责，此举可能导致高额罚款，并使竞选重点复杂化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/eu-to-slam-france-over-budget-deficit-adding-to-political-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国无家可归者人数上升 住房危机仍是选民关注的焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/rising-uk-homelessness-keeps-housing-crunch-in-front-of-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国无家可归人口激增已成为住房危机的另一个症状，住房危机在下个月大选之前将这一问题推上了政治议程，活动人士表示，主要政党在提供可负担住房方面做得不够。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/rising-uk-homelessness-keeps-housing-crunch-in-front-of-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国央行再次提出限制 140 亿美元刺激计划的提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/thai-central-bank-renews-case-to-limit-14-billion-cash-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行仍然坚决反对政府向几乎所有成年公民发放近 140 亿美元现金以重振消费活动的计划，称谨慎的做法是把重点放在有需要的人身上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/thai-central-bank-renews-case-to-limit-14-billion-cash-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 03:37:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>李克强访问马来西亚，安华平衡中美利益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/premier-li-visits-malaysia-as-anwar-balances-us-china-interests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国务院总理李强于周二晚间开始对马来西亚进行为期三天的访问，北京希望加深与马来西亚的关系，在中美竞争加剧的情况下，马来西亚一直保持中立。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/premier-li-visits-malaysia-as-anwar-balances-us-china-interests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙称法国“沉默的大多数”反对极端主义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/macron-says-snap-election-was-needed-to-avoid-chaos-in-france</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法新社周二援引法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的话说，反对极端主义造成的混乱的“沉默的大多数”存在。尽管在 6 月 30 日开始的立法选举之前，他的政党在民意调查中一直落后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/macron-says-snap-election-was-needed-to-avoid-chaos-in-france</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 18:51:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡告诉美国‘给我们工具，我们将完成工作’</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/netanyahu-tells-us-give-us-the-tools-we-ll-finish-the-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡表示，总统乔·拜登在与哈马斯的战争中扣留武器，因为他的国家正在“为生存而战”，但白宫否认了这一指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/netanyahu-tells-us-give-us-the-tools-we-ll-finish-the-job</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:44:20 GMT</pubDate>
